readme:
# A10 Networks ACOS Configuration support

This language package provides ACOS Configuration highlighting for Atom.
Currently only Running Config highlighting is supported

![screenshot](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mischapeters/a10-networks-syntax/master/a10networks.png)

### Extensions supported
- .cfg
- .conf
- .log

The grammar also matches on the first line present in a `show tech` or a cut&paste that starts with a `!`.

Contributions are welcome! Fork and pull!

This grammar package is very loosely based on:
- [Language Cisco](https://github.com/diogoandre/language-cisco)
- [Atom Cisco Syntax](https://github.com/asbjornenge/atom-cisco-syntax)
